  "What does 'unification' mean in the context of Maxwell's work?": "",
  "Showing that electricity and magnetism are aspects of a single electromagnetic force": "",
  "Combining Newton's laws of motion with the law of universal gravitation": "",
  "Proving that all four fundamental forces of nature are actually the same force": "",
  "Merging the wave theory and particle theory of light into quantum mechanics": "",
  "Maxwell showed that electricity and magnetism are not separate phenomena but two aspects of a single electromagnetic force. His equations describe how electric and magnetic fields create and sustain each other.": "",
  "What is 'permittivity of free space' (ε₀)?": "",
