  "That gravity can carry information between objects at the speed of light": "",
  "Maxwell predicted that oscillating electric and magnetic fields propagate as electromagnetic waves through space at the speed of light. Phones use radio-frequency EM waves to send and receive data wirelessly.": "",
  "A student reads that Maxwell derived the speed of light from electric and magnetic constants. Which formula did he use?": "",
