  "c = √(μ₀/ε₀) using the ratio of both constants": "",
  "c = μ₀ + ε₀ using the sum of both constants together": "",
  "Maxwell showed that c = 1/√(μ₀ε₀), where μ₀ is the permeability of free space and ε₀ is the permittivity. Plugging in measured values gives c ≈ 3 × 10⁸ m/s — matching the measured speed of light.": "",
